messages.text: What? You gotta give me more than that.
some bad shit just went down
Still? Did you get into the party?
yeah. but it’s definitely over now.
Quit being cagey. I need DETAILS.
cops are here. that’s all i know.
What else is new? No one is gonna care that the cops showed up.
there’s like a bunch of them. and detectives. ambulances. fire trucks.
Okay...I can maybe work with this. How many cops would you say?
Okay. I’m gonna call the hotel. See if they can tell me anything.
yeah. but my memory card is running low.
what am I an amateur mel? I brought several but i’ve been shooting all night
so most of them are full
Ugh hotel isn’t giving me anything.
security is trying to keep fans out
oh yeah. hundreds of em. they’ve been here all night.
most of em are 14 year old girls
Jesus it’s 3am! Where are their parents?!
How tense is it? How are the cops acting?
idk, concerned maybe? How do cops usually act??
Okay Grady, I need you to be extremely observant.
I don’t have time to send a reporter down there, so you’re my eyes and ears.
Don’t forget you’re a paparazzi photographer.
they just rolled out a body bag on a gurney
Get some of crying fans. Just in case.
In case it’s the little twerp inside.
jesus melissa, the kid might be dead
But maybe not. Find out who’s in that body bag.
how?? i’m not gonna go unzip it!
Hang around the cops. Maybe you’ll hear something.
they’re being pretty hush hush about it.
made me leave the area so i didn’t hear much
Grady, if that body belongs to Jamie, I need to know ASAP.
We can’t let EW release this before us.
My head will be on a fucking platter.
the gurney is stuck. they can’t get it into the ambulance.
okay i’m over by the detectives
She hasn’t been in the public eye for months! Was she there tonight?
You always had a thing for her though.
i’m serious tho. her hair was really long.
Did you at least get a photo of her?
Why do I even pay you?
because no one else will do this shit job
Okay, so they suspect Serena Diamond. For murder, I’m guessing.
You’d better fucking stay Grady, or I’m not paying you at all!
And I’m definitely getting a promotion.
What do you mean? Wasn’t she there earlier?
they’re locking down the premises till they find her
She’s on the run! This is incredible!
Don’t be like that. I’ll pay you over time.
At least get a room for the rest of the night.
are you high? there’s a murderer loose in this hotel!
Well, we don’t know if she did it. Innocent before proven guilty!
i’m getting the hell out of here as soon as they let me
Can you at least get a statement from someone there?
looks like they’re letting us leave. i’ll upload photos when i get home.
Did you at least get a photo of the body??
Fine. I should’ve sent Chris on this assignment. He has no morals.
Driving now. Goodnight and good raisins.
Siri autocorrected me. I meant good riddance.
I want a bonus for my emotional trauma.
TMZ Breaking News! By TMZ Editor Melissa Brute.
Our sources report that international pop star JAMIE has been found dead in his hotel room at the Sunset Hotel in downtown Los Angeles, early Sunday morning.
The body was found following a raucous, celebrity-studded party in celebration of the star’s 21st birthday.
Police suspect foul play, and are questioning those in attendance.
The most prominent suspect is actress Serena Diamond, who slipped out of the limelight after her very public breakup with the pop star in 2015.
